    <!-- IE10 viewport hack for Surface/desktop Windows 8 bug -->

    <script>
(function($) {

if (!String.prototype.startsWith) {
    String.prototype.startsWith = function(searchString, position){
      position = position || 0;
      return this.substr(position, searchString.length) === searchString;
  };
}

    /**
     * Splash once and for all
     */
    if (localStorage.getItem("splashed") === null) {
        //alert("not splashed yet!");
        $('#disclaimer-splash').fadeIn("slow");
    } else {
        $('#disclaimer-splash').hide();

    }
    $("#agreedBtn").click(function() {
        $('#disclaimer-splash').fadeOut("slow");
        localStorage.setItem("splashed", "splashed");
    });
    
    $("#tou").click(function () {
        $('#disclaimer-splash').fadeIn("slow");
    });

  /**
   * polyfill for html5 form attr
   */

  // detect if browser supports this
  var sampleElement = $('[form]').get(0);
  var isIE11 = !(window.ActiveXObject) && "ActiveXObject" in window;
  if (sampleElement && window.HTMLFormElement && sampleElement.form instanceof HTMLFormElement && !isIE11) {
    // browser supports it, no need to fix
    return;
  }

  /**
   * Append a field to a form
   *
   */
  $.fn.appendField = function(data) {
    // for form only
    if (!this.is('form')) return;

    // wrap data
    if (!$.isArray(data) && data.name && data.value) {
      data = [data];
    }

    var $form = this;

    // attach new params
    $.each(data, function(i, item) {
      $('<input/>')
        .attr('type', 'hidden')
        .attr('name', item.name)
        .val(item.value).appendTo($form);
    });

    return $form;
  };

  /**
   * Find all input fields with form attribute point to jQuery object
   *
   */
  $('form[id]').submit(function(e) {
    var $form = $(this);
    // serialize data
    var data = $('[form='+ $form.attr('id') + ']').serializeArray();
    // append data to form
    $form.appendField(data);
  }).each(function() {
    var form = this,
      $form = $(form),
      $fields = $('[form=' + $form.attr('id') + ']');

    $fields.filter('button, input').filter('[type=reset],[type=submit]').click(function() {
      var type = this.type.toLowerCase();
      if (type === 'reset') {
        // reset form
        form.reset();
        // for elements outside form
        $fields.each(function() {
          this.value = this.defaultValue;
          this.checked = this.defaultChecked;
        }).filter('select').each(function() {
          $(this).find('option').each(function() {
            this.selected = this.defaultSelected;
          });
        });
      } else if (type.match(/^submit|image$/i)) {
        $(form).appendField({name: this.name, value: this.value}).submit();
      }
    });
  });


})(jQuery);
    </script>

        $(document).ready(function(){

            function gleamyround(value, decimals) {
                if (isNaN(parseFloat(value))) {
                    return "";
                } else {
                    var v = parseFloat(value);
                    var roundedv = Number(Math.round(value + 'e' + decimals) + 'e-' + decimals);
                    return roundedv.toString();
                }
            };
            function find_entry_name_by_id(id, arr) {
                for (i = 0; i < arr.length; i++) {
                    if (arr[i].id == id) {
                        return arr[i].name;
                    }
                }
            };

            var dt_allin = $("#all_input_table").DataTable({
                sDom: "tp",
                initComplete: function () {
                    this.api().columns().every( function () {
                        var column = this;
                        var title =  $(column.header()).html();
                        if (title == "system" || title == "orientation" || title == "feedgroup") {

                            var select_container = $('<div class="col-lg-3"></div>');
                            var select = $('<select class="form-control"><option value=""></option></select>')
                                .appendTo(select_container)
                                .on('change', function () {
                                    var val = $.fn.dataTable.util.escapeRegex(
                                        $(this).val()
                                    );

                                    column
                                        .search(val ? '^' + val + '$' : '', true, false)
                                        .draw();
                                });
                            select_container.appendTo($("#customfilters"));
                            column.data().unique().sort().each(function (d, j) {
                                if (d != ""){
                                    $(select).append('<option value="' + d + '">' + d + '</option>');
                                }

                            });
                        }
                    });
                },
                autoWidth: false,
                scrollX: true,
                paging: false,
                data: allinput_data,
                order: [[2, 'asc']],
                createdRow: function( row, data, dataIndex ) {
                    if ( data["feedgroup_id"] > 0 ) {
                        var tmprationtag = "RA_"+data["specie"]+"_"+data["production_system_id"]+"_"+data["orientation_id"]+"_"+data["feedgroup_id"];
                        $(row).addClass(tmprationtag);
                    }
                    if ( data["manuremanagement_id"] > 0 ) {
                        var tmprationtag = "MA_"+data["specie"]+"_"+data["production_system_id"]+"_"+data["orientation_id"];
                        $(row).addClass(tmprationtag);
                    }
                },
                columns: [
                    { data: 'specie', name: 'specie', title: 'Specie', visible: false },
                    { data: 'module', name: 'module', title: 'module', visible: false },
                    { data: 'order', name: 'order', title: 'order', visible: false },
                    { data: 'production_system', name: 'system', title: 'system' },
                    { data: 'orientation', name: 'orientation', title: 'orientation' },
                    { data: 'feedgroup', name: 'feedgroup', title: 'feedgroup'},
                    { data: 'name', name: 'name', title: 'parameter' },
                    { data: 'unit', name: 'unit', title: 'unit' },
                    { data: 'str_value', name: 'value', title: 'default', render: $.fn.dataTable.render.number( ',', '.', 2 ) }
                    
                    
                ]
            });
            dt_allin.$('input').on("focus", function() {
                this.oldvalue = this.value;
            });
            var zerobuttons = $('button.zerome');
            $(zerobuttons).on("click", function(e){
                $(this).tooltip('destroy');
                var tmpsc = $(this).attr("name");
                var matchinginputs = dt_allin.$('tr').find('td.'+tmpsc).find('input:visible');
                $(matchinginputs).each(function(e){
                    this.oldvalue = this.value;
                    $(this).val(0);
                    $(this).trigger("change");

                });
                $(this).attr("title", "set all values to 0");
                $(this).attr("data-toggle", "tooltip");
                $(this).tooltip();
            });

            var fromprevbuttons = $('button.fromprev');
            $(fromprevbuttons).on("click", function(e){

                $(this).tooltip('destroy');
                var tmpsc = $(this).attr("name");
                var matchinginputs = dt_allin.$('tr').find('td.'+tmpsc).find('input:visible');
                $(matchinginputs).each(function(e){
                    this.oldvalue = this.value;
                    sourceinput = $(this).parent("td").prev().children("input")
                    if (sourceinput.length){
                        $(this).val($(sourceinput).val());
                        $(this).trigger("change");
                    } else{
                        defaultval = $(this).parent("td").prev().html();
                        //$(this).val(parseFloat(defaultval.replace(/\s/g, '').replace(",", ".")))
                        if (isNaN(parseFloat(defaultval.replace(/\s/g, '').replace(/\,/g, "")))) {
                            $(this).val(0);
                        }
                        else {
                            $(this).val(parseFloat(defaultval.replace(/\s/g, '').replace(/\,/g, "")));
                        }
                        $(this).trigger("change");
                    }

                });
                $(this).attr("title", "copy from previous column");
                $(this).attr("data-toggle", "tooltip");
                $(this).tooltip();

            });

            var fromxlbuttons = $('button.xlpaste');
            $(fromxlbuttons).on("click", function(e){
                $(this).tooltip('destroy');
                var tmpsc = $(this).attr("name");
                var matchinginputs = dt_allin.$('tr').find('td.'+tmpsc).find('input:visible');

                navigator.clipboard.readText().then(
                    function(txt){
                        //alert(txt);
                        var xlis = txt.split(/\r?\n/);
                        //alert(ks[0]);
                        var i;
                        for (i = 0; i < xlis.length-1; i++) {
                            var e = matchinginputs[i];
                            e.oldvalue = e.value;
                            if (isNaN(parseFloat(xlis[i].replace(/\s/g, '').replace(/\,/g, "")))) {
                                $(e).val(0);
                            }
                            else {
                                $(e).val(parseFloat(xlis[i].replace(/\s/g, '').replace(/\,/g, "")));
                            }
                            $(e).trigger("change");
                        }
                    }
                );

                $(this).attr("title", "paste values from clipboard");
                $(this).attr("data-toggle", "tooltip");
                $(this).tooltip();

            });


            dt_allin.$('input').on("change", function(e) {
                var colname = $(this).attr("id").split("_")[0];
                var classnames = $(this).closest("tr").attr("class").split(" ");
                this.value= this.value.replace(",", ".");
                for (var i=0;i<classnames.length;i++){
                    if (percentset_list_keys.indexOf(classnames[i])>=0){
                        //update ration sum
                        var tmpration = percentset_list[classnames[i]];
                        var tmprationsum = parseFloat(tmpration[colname]);
                        if (isNaN(parseFloat(this.oldvalue))) {
                            this.oldvalue = "0";
                        }
                        if (isNaN(parseFloat(this.value))) {
                            this.value = "0";
                        }
                        tmprationsum = tmprationsum - parseFloat(this.oldvalue) + parseFloat(this.value);
                        tmpration[colname] = tmprationsum;
                        percentset_list[classnames[i]] = tmpration;

                        //Is ration sum 100 or not?
                        var matchinginputs = $('tr.'+classnames[i]).find('td.'+colname).find('input');
                        $(matchinginputs).tooltip('destroy');
                        if (Math.round(tmprationsum) != 100) {

                            var leftover = Math.round(tmprationsum)-100;
                            if (leftover > 0) {
                                var ttt = leftover + "% should be cut off";
                            } else {
                                var ttt = leftover + "% is missing";
                            }
                            $(matchinginputs).css("border", "1px orange solid");
                            $(matchinginputs).attr("title", ttt);
                            $(matchinginputs).attr("data-toggle", "tooltip");
                            $(matchinginputs).tooltip();
                        } else {
                            $(matchinginputs).css("border", "");
                        }
                    }
                }

                $(this).css("color","blue");

                if (this.value.length && isNaN(parseFloat(this.value))){
                    alert("invalid decimal value!");
                    $(this).css("color","red");
                }
                this.oldvalue = this.value;
            });

            function filter_full_datatable(e, clsname) {

                var sel = "."+clsname;
                $(sel).addClass("notselected");
                $(e).removeClass("notselected");

                selectionid = parseInt(e.id.replace("menumod", ""));

                if (clsname == "speciemenuimg"){
                    selected_specie = selectionid;
                    $("#dataset_specie_title").text(find_entry_name_by_id(selected_specie, species_list));
                } else {
                    selected_module = selectionid;
                    $("#dataset_module_title").text(find_entry_name_by_id(selected_module, modules_list)+": ");
                }

                $.fn.dataTable.ext.search.pop();
                $.fn.dataTableExt.afnFiltering.push(
                        function(oSettings, aData, iDataIndex ) {
                            if (aData[0] == selected_specie && aData[1] == selected_module) {
                                return true;
                            }
                            return false;
                });

                dt_allin.column("feedgroup:name").visible(selected_module == 2).draw();

            };

            $('[data-toggle="tooltip"]').tooltip();

            $( ".speciemenuimg" ).on( "click", function() {
                filter_full_datatable(this, "speciemenuimg");
            });
            $( ".modulemenuimg" ).on( "click", function() {
                filter_full_datatable(this, "modulemenuimg");
            });

            $("#aprev_module").on("click", function (){
                module_selected_idx = module_selected_idx-1;
                if (module_selected_idx < 0) {
                    module_selected_idx = modules_list.length-1;
                }
                selected_module = modules_list[module_selected_idx].id;
                $("#menumod"+selected_module).trigger("click");
            });
            $("#aprev_specie").on("click", function (){
                specie_selected_idx = specie_selected_idx-1;
                if (specie_selected_idx < 0) {
                    specie_selected_idx = species_list.length-1;
                }
                selected_specie = species_list[specie_selected_idx].id;
                $("#"+selected_specie).trigger("click");
            });
            $("#anext_module").on("click", function (){
                module_selected_idx = module_selected_idx+1;
                if (module_selected_idx >= modules_list.length) {
                    module_selected_idx = 0;
                }
                selected_module = modules_list[module_selected_idx].id;

                $("#menumod"+selected_module).trigger("click");
            });
            $("#anext_specie").on("click", function (){
                specie_selected_idx = specie_selected_idx+1;
                if (specie_selected_idx >= species_list.length) {
                    specie_selected_idx = 0;
                }
                selected_specie = species_list[specie_selected_idx].id;

                $("#"+selected_specie).trigger("click");
            });

            $("#menumod"+selected_module).trigger("click");
            $("#"+selected_specie).trigger("click");

            $('#submitform').submit(function(eventObj) {
                for (var r in percentset_list) {
                    for (var sc in percentset_list[r]) {
                        var tmpscsum = Math.round(percentset_list[r][sc]);
                        if (tmpscsum != 100) {
                            //alert("Some set of percentages are not equal to 100: please correct the input fields highlighted in orange");
                            alert("Some set of percentages ("+r+"-"+sc+")are not equal to 100: please correct the input fields highlighted in orange");
                            return false;
                        }
                    }
                }
                on();
                //TODO: ensure that non modified rounded inputs are reverted to their original value??
                $(this).append(dt_allin.$('input, select'));
                return true;
            });
        });

        function on() {
            document.getElementById("overlay").style.display = "block";
        };


        function off() {
            document.getElementById("overlay").style.display = "none";
        };

    </script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/2.7.2/Chart.min.js"></script>

<div id="overlay">
    <div class="overlay-content">
        <h1>Calculations at work.... Please, stay with us.</h1>
    </div>
</div>

      $(document).ready(function(){
        $('[data-toggle="tooltip"]').tooltip();
      });
      </script>
